post.content:
Dear Band Families,

We need more volunteers for Uniform Turn In from 6pm to 8pm on Tuesday and Wednesday next week (about 4 people each evening). We really need the help in order to keep wait times down. If you can help please contact Anthony at aja@aamatolaw.com.

Thanks,
Becky Humes
Band Booster Corresponding Secretary
